Text:
Win 7 x64.

Installed app, then ran "DVDFab 7.x Registration.exe"

Black terminal window appeared, files were copied. then it reports in green text:
"Sorry must be a problem, please report this error to author.."

I tried copying and running "DVDFab 7.x Registration.exe" from the DVDfab install folder.

Any ideas?
Also tried running DVDFAB.exe. I get pop up intro screen showing m that I have trial license for all programs. When I click "start DVDfab" nothing happens.

Installed on Win 7 Ultimate.  Works fine.

Copy "DVDFab 7.x Registration.exe" to installation folder, and then run as Administrator.
